<HEAD>People In The News</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY44</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Diana Ross has given birth to her fifth
child, a boy, the singer's publicist said.
   It was the 44-year-old singer's second child with husband Arne
Naess Jr., according to publicist Elliot Mintz.
   He said the boy was born Friday, but declined to say where the
